{"tid":93976,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【短片】【明星股上市】袁彌明旗下「百貨店」謀創業板上市","createTime":"2017-01-25T00:24:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T00:37:48.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7c62cda162a377214fecf0887767bece7447cbe7","tid":93976,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:24:15.000Z","msg":"【短片】【明星股上市】袁彌明旗下「百貨店」謀創業板上市<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/082332_8b439839d3cd027db9fb67c2b7da93ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F082332_8b439839d3cd027db9fb67c2b7da93ad.jpg&h=24c5ac29&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/082332_7907112cfd0d7361c50d9e897b190814.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F082332_7907112cfd0d7361c50d9e897b190814.jpg&h=dd79c218&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/082333_7907112cfd0d7361c50d9e897b190814.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F082333_7907112cfd0d7361c50d9e897b190814.jpg&h=356e52b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/082333_836916f5bbefccf5572db923606980cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F082333_836916f5bbefccf5572db923606980cd.jpg&h=5e07e7e3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/082334_836916f5bbefccf5572db923606980cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F082334_836916f5bbefccf5572db923606980cd.jpg&h=abf21e47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【新增影片】<br />\n<br />\n已離開政界的前港姐袁彌明旗下「彌明生活百貨」剛遞交創業板上市申請，獨家保薦人為金利豐。該股現時於銅鑼灣、旺角、尖沙咀、沙田、荃灣、元朗共有6家零售店，出售護膚品、化妝品、食品及保健產品。<br />\n<br />\n袁彌明自任主席兼行政總裁，其夫林雨陽則任非執行董事。袁彌明胞姊袁彌望（43歲）則出任執董，與袁彌望同住的張肇漢（36歲）亦擔任非執董。招股書形容袁彌明為「傑出的社交媒體偶像」，林雨陽本身於2012至2016年期間，為網台Hong Kong New Media行政總裁。<br />\n<br />\n截至去年9月底，該股半年收入4772萬元，亦為「Synergie Skin」、「pHion」等品牌的港澳地區獨家分銷商。<br />\n<br />\n集資所得將增設零售店、翻新現有零售店、在香港購置一個倉庫、擴大產品組合、增強網上營銷等。集團計劃於2019年3月底，在香港開設6家新零售店。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56218521&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56218521%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170125&d=KnADQkSl2sxDDPCCFkWTswv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=673e263e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56218521%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170125&h=44ac6416\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56218521&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170125</a>"},{"pid":"1eeb7b6163d41e51d8a53fcf8ca23bcb3e934748","tid":93976,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:37:48.000Z","msg":"搵老襯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}